# Privacy-first allowlist: only the distributable tool is tracked.
*

!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!LICENSE
!README.md
!SUPPORTED_MEGATRON_VERSIONS.md
!pyproject.toml

!.github/
!.github/workflows/
!.github/workflows/ci.yml

!memory_fragmentation/
!memory_fragmentation/*.py
!memory_fragmentation/README.md
!tests/
!tests/*.py

# Never publish generated or potentially sensitive artifacts.
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*.pickle
**/*.pkl
**/memory-traces/
**/analysis/
**/log/
**/data/
*.egg-info/
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
